&lt;h1 id=&#34;outside-the-lab&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#outside-the-lab&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Outside the lab&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
