较为著名的背包密码有 Merkle-Hellman 方案（Hiding information and signatures in trapdoor knapsacks，已被攻破）和 Nasako-Murakami 方案（Knapsack Public-Key Cryptosystem Using Chinese Remainder Theorem）。&lt;/p&gt;
